Monks these two slander the Tathagata
Which two
He who explains what was not said or spoken by the Tathagata as said or spoken by the Tathagata
And he who explains what was said or spoken by the Tathagata as not said or spoken by the Tathagata
These are two who slander the Tathagata
Monks these two are fools
Which two
The one who doesn't see his transgression as a transgression and the one who doesn't rightfully pardon another who has confessed his transgression
These two are fools
These two are wise people
Which two
The one who sees his transgression as a transgression and the one who rightfully pardons another who has confessed his transgression
These two are wise people
