Then a large number of wandering sectarians came and said to me 'Friend Anurādha the Tathāgata  the supreme man the superlative man attainer of the superlative attainment  being described is described with these four positions The Tathāgata exists after death does not exist after death both does  does not exist after death neither exists nor does not exist after death'
